        <item>
            <title>乘客坐九巴大聲播片屢勸不改，司機一句秒殺令他收聲</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/21/bus-playing-video-with-loud-sound/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=bus-playing-video-with-loud-sound</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/21/bus-playing-video-with-loud-sound/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 06:55:50 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[巴士]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293267</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前有乘客在車廂內大聲聊天，九巴司機無法忍受下停車開咪怒罵乘客足足一分鐘才能讓乘客收聲（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/kmb-tun-mun/fun-tech/">相關報道</a>），想不到「人類總要重複同樣的錯誤」，日前又發生類似事件。網上流傳一段九巴司機開咪高峯責罵乘客的影片。影片中顯示一名乘客似乎在車廂內大聲聊天，面對乘客無視其多次提醒，司機最終選擇停車並使用車內咪高峯，發出近一分鐘的怒罵，成功讓那些喧嘩的乘客收聲，車廂也迅速回復平靜。</p><p>網上有影片流傳，顯示 2 月 11 日一名九巴 P968 乘客在車廂內公然大聲播放影片，嚴重影響其他乘客。司機見狀廣播勸阻，多次勸阻無效司機終於忍無可忍，果斷開咪喝斥要求乘客停止播片，繼續播放就會報警並拒絕開車。</p><p>影片源自 Facebook 羣組「<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1sur9pj xkrqix3 xzsf02u x1s688f" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/646949689010059/?__cft__[0]=AZXGvVemyYCZMA2HC7YHLKqDCN72k8qD10En972FJIVbrr6pW4osVJnZep9LdOj_TgRIXgVHqK2Tpy-OGaKMtbFzqc20a_d1Ued9mbTSRsblYH5hIXjYE7nVXx7PzHlQ5jFPOscC_sT5GXT3K-oFgrZnPzKJu4HvXpEPfIzG_WuW-K1wv0BCLhltkE0we8oe41k&amp;__tn__=-UC%2CP-R"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs">香港突發事故報料區及討論區</span></a>」，事發時一名乘客用手機外放影片，音量極大，刺耳聲響影響車廂安寧，司機透過廣播多次提醒保持車廂安靜」和「調低手提電腦音量」，惟對方依舊充耳不聞，態度頑固。見對方屢勸不改，司機最終決定開咪斥責，要求乘客停止播片，繼續播放就會停車兼報警，他就可以「慢慢賺補水」。上傳影片的網民引述乘客回應指：「使唔使咁串」，司機就表示：「點解咁串係因為按法例報警處理，多謝你畀到支持我」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120441-493x580.jpg" alt="" width="493" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120441-493x580.jpg 493w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120441.jpg 632w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 493px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz x1sur9pj xkrqix3 xzsf02u x1s688f" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/646949689010059/?__cft__[0]=AZXGvVemyYCZMA2HC7YHLKqDCN72k8qD10En972FJIVbrr6pW4osVJnZep9LdOj_TgRIXgVHqK2Tpy-OGaKMtbFzqc20a_d1Ued9mbTSRsblYH5hIXjYE7nVXx7PzHlQ5jFPOscC_sT5GXT3K-oFgrZnPzKJu4HvXpEPfIzG_WuW-K1wv0BCLhltkE0we8oe41k&amp;__tn__=-UC%2CP-R"><span class="html-span xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs">香港突發事故報料區及討論區</span></a></p><p>影片在網上廣傳後掀起討論，網民力撐司機，認為他做法值得讚揚。有留言認為乘客應該自律，不要發出不必要噪音影響車長專注、騷擾其他乘客。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120207-694x82.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="82" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120207-694x82.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022120207.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有人為巴士司機抱打不平，直言：「應該平時忍夠啲痴線佬成日播嘈（噪）音」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022115954-694x143.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="143" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022115954-694x143.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022115954.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>香港大學法律與科技研究中心指，根據《道路交通 (公共服務車輛) 規例》(第 374D 章) 第 46(1)(n)(i) 條，公共巴士之乘客或有意乘搭該等車輛的人，不得在車內或車上的時候使用或操作任何嘈吵的器具、樂器或任何留聲機、收音機或錄音機，而滋擾到任何其他人。任何人無合理辯解而違反第 46 條，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處罰款 $3,000 及監禁 6 個月。</p><p>有興趣觀看司機如何反擊的朋友可以點擊下面連結：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/posts/2443225162715827/">https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/posts/2443225162715827/</a></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F813831777123798%2Fvideos%2F1152833099851264%2F%3Fidorvanity%3D1060857804356998&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=267&amp;t=0" width="267" height="476" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe><br />
圖片來源：<a href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fd/V6P8_KMB_P968_18-07-2021%281%29.jpg">Wikipedia</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/HKGuy/posts/2443225162715827/">香港突發事故報料區及討論區</a>、<a href="https://www.clic.org.hk/zh/topics/traffic_law/public_transport/public_bus/passenger_plays_loud_music">香港大學法律與科技研究中心</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
